                 <font style=\"color: #13152f!important; font-weight: bold;\">Ashley W.<\/font> \n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn3.emoji.gg\/emojis\/9796-verified.png\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" alt=\"Verified\"> \n                        <font style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #13152f;\">Verified<\/font>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                <!-- Additional Reviews -->\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★★★<\/div>\n                    <div class=\"description\">Burn time is no joke — this candle lasts forever. Really impressed with the quality and packaging.<\/div>\n                    <div class=\"name\">\n                        <font style=\"color: #13152f!important; font-weight: bold;\">Daniel K.<\/font>\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn3.emoji.gg\/emojis\/9796-verified.png\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" alt=\"Verified\">\n                        <font style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #13152f;\">Verified<\/font>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★★★<\/div>\n                    <div class=\"description\">The candle feels very clean and natural. No headaches or harsh smells like some other brands.<\/div>\n                    <div class=\"name\">\n                        <font style=\"color: #13152f!important; font-weight: bold;\">Lauren P.<\/font>\n                        <img src=\"https:\/\/cdn3.emoji.gg\/emojis\/9796-verified.png\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" alt=\"Verified\">\n                        <font style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #13152f;\">Verified<\/font>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n                <div class=\"swiper-slide\">\n                    <div class=\"rating\">★★★★★<\/div>\n                    <div class=\"description\">Easy to use, unique design, and smells fantastic. This has 